<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَالحُشِّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَتَكْسِيرُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَا يُسَنُّ غَسْلُهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَتُجْزِئُ حَصَاةٌ نَجِسَةٌ مَعَ الكَرَاهَةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- فَيَرْمِي جَمْرَةَ العَقَبَةِ وَحْدَهَا بِسَبْعٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُشْتَرَطُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> الرَّمْيُ، فَلَا يُجْزِئُ الوَضْعُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَكَوْنُهُ وَاحِدَةً بَعْدَ أُخْرَى.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- يَرْفَعُ يُمْنَاهُ مَعَ كُلِّ حَصَاةٍ حَتَّى يُرَى بَيَاضُ إِبْطِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَيُكَبِّرُ مَعَ كُلِّ حَصَاةٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- ثُمَّ يَنْحَرُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَيَحْلِقُ أَوْ يُقَصِّرُ مِنْ جَمِيعِ شَعْرِهِ، لَا مِنْ كُلِّ شَعْرَةٍ بِعَيْنِهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>